conky-manager (2.3.3) trusty; urgency=low

  * Added appdata.xml file
  
  * Fixed: Applying wallpaper to Cinnamon desktop with scaling option 'none' can result in an empty/black background

  * Fixed: Create empty startup script if widgets are not enabled
  
  * While generating previews for all 'missing' cases, generate previews for those widgets also which have common 'preview.xxx' file
  
  * Combo for switching between Widget List and Theme List is replaced by toggle buttons for single-click switching
  
  * Fixed: After generating preview, selected list item will remain selected instead of reloading the list
  
